  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 text-center">
    <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6">
      Ready to Transform Your Career?
    </h2>
    <p class="text-xl mb-8 max-w-3xl mx-auto text-blue-100">
      Join thousands of Ohio residents who have built successful careers through our WIOA-approved programs. 
      Free training, job placement assistance, and industry certifications await.
    </p>
    
    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center mb-12">
      <a 
        href="/eligibility-check.html" 
        class="bg-secondary-500 hover:bg-secondary-600 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-semibold text-lg transition-colors duration-200"
      >
        Check Your Eligibility Now
