        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Start Your Career</h3>
        <p class="text-blue-100">Graduate with certification and job placement</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-blue-400 border-opacity-30">
      <p class="text-blue-100 text-sm">
        <strong>Next enrollment starts:</strong> January 15, 2025 | 
